<div class="content">

<h2><a href="./" title="GStreamer MP3 Encoding mini-HowTo">GStreamer MP3 Encoding mini-HowTo *</a></h2>

<div style="text-align: right;"><small><i>* or how to enable mp3 output in <a href="http://soundconverter.berlios.de">SoundConverter</a></i></small></div>


<h3>
<img style="width: 32x; height: 32px;" alt="Ubuntu" src="ubuntu-logo.png" align="middle" hspace="8">
Ubuntu</h3>

<p>
Add  <a href="http://help.ubuntu.com/community/RestrictedFormats">multiverse sources</a>.<br>
Install package <b>gstreamer0.10-plugins-ugly-multiverse</b>.<br>

</p>

<p>

<h3>
<img style="width: 32x; height: 32px;" alt="Mandriva" src="mandriva-logo.png" align="middle" hspace="8">
Mandriva</h3>
Add PLF sources with <a href="http://easyurpmi.zarb.org/">EasyUrpmi</a>.<br>
And then install package <b>gstreamer-lame</b>.<br>
<br>
</p>

<p>
<h3>
<img style="width: 32x; height: 32px;" alt="Fedora" src="fedora-logo.png" align="middle" hspace="8">
Fedora</h3>
Add <a href="http://rpm.livna.org">livna repository</a>. 
<br>
Install <b>gstreamer-plugins-ugly</b>.<br>
<br>
</p>

<p>
<h3>
<img style="width: 32x; height: 32px;" alt="Gentoo" src="gentoo-logo.png" align="middle" hspace="8">
Gentoo</h3>
Install package <b>gst-plugins-lame</b>.<br>
<br>
</p>

<p>
<h3>
<img style="width: 32x; height: 32px;" alt="Debian" src="debian-logo.png" align="middle" hspace="8">
Debian</h3>
Add the <a href="http://www.debian-multimedia.org">debian-multimedia repository</a> to apt sources.<br>
Install packages <b>gstreamer0.10-lame</b>.<br>
<br>
</p>

</div>

